Some influencers will do just about anything for engagement and growth but this time their followers weren't impressed. Influencers were slammed on Instagram for turning much-needed medical masks into bikinis in a wasteful trend while many healthcare workers struggle to find any protective gear. The bikinis are known as quarankinis and they are a new trend that is on social media during the coronavirus outbreak. The trend comes after the WHO asked healthy people not to wear face masks because there is little evidence that they help and they would be better used by healthcare workers and patients who test positive for Covid-19.  